OL,3,CLocal elections 2026: The results for
OL,4,CYorkshire and Lincolnshire
OL,6,FMillions of people have been casting
OL,7,Ftheir votes in a series of crucial
OL,8,Flocal elections across the country.
OL,10,FThe results will affect who has
OL,11,Fcontrol over things like neighbourhood
OL,12,Fbin collections, road repairs,
OL,13,Fschooling and planning.
OL,15,FBut, in an increasingly fragmented
OL,16,Fpolitical environment, the outcomes
OL,17,Fcould also have far-reaching
OL,18,Fconsequences at a national level.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/7
