OL,3,CLocal elections 2026: The results for
OL,4,CYorkshire and Lincolnshire
OL,6,FIn Yorkshire and Lincolnshire, seats
OL,7,Fon 10 councils are up for grabs and
OL,8,Fcounts are taking place on Friday and
OL,9,FSaturday.
OL,11,FThere are "all out" elections in
OL,12,FBarnsley, Bradford, Kirklees,
OL,13,FCalderdale and Wakefield - meaning all
OL,14,Fthe seats will be contested.
OL,16,FIn Leeds, Sheffield, Hull, Lincoln and
OL,17,FNorth East Lincolnshire a third of
OL,18,Fseats will be decided, but tight
OL,19,Fmajorities mean small shifts could
OL,20,Fsignificantly change the councils'
OL,21,Fmake-up.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
